headline: Morgan Stanley Emerging Markets Debt Fund, Inc. Announces Updated Investment Disclosure
summary: NEW YORK, December 06, 2024--Morgan Stanley Investment Management today announced that, effective immediately, the Morgan Stanley Emerging Markets Debt Fund, Inc. (NYSE: MSD) (the "Fund") is no longer limited to investing up to 35% of its total assets in debt securities of corporate issuers located in or organized under the laws of emerging countries.

headline: Hiring Bounced Back With 227,000 Jobs Added Last Month
summary: The labor market bounced back last month, as workers sidelined by storms got back on the job, and as thousands of striking Boeing employees returned to work.
